# Build output
/target/
**/target/
*.exe
*.pdb
*.dll
*.obj
*.ilk
*.exp
*.lib

# Live cargo config (the nightly LTO config breaks stable builds — ship the
# .example instead; see BUILDING-LTO.md)
.cargo/config.toml

# Profile-guided-optimization raw data (the canonical profile IS committed at
# _pgo/dual.profdata; the old lowercase pgo/ clang-only profiles are superseded)
*.profraw
/pgo/

# Build logs
*.log

# Obsidian-vault research notebooks (they live in the Obsidian vault, with working
# wikilinks; excluded here so the public repo has no broken [[links]])
/optimization-journey.md
/performance-architecture.md

# OS / editor cruft
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
.DS_Store
*.swp
.vscode/
.idea/
